Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.07,0:00:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初  真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人一起去学校  一起拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟君和我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…还有高槻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个察觉到二鸟君适合穿女装的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知从何时起  高槻同学总跟在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾一度以为他们疏远了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时他们又和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐那份也放在里面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思去二年级的教室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐走得太急了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈并没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个一年级生？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是那张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学典礼时穿立领的女生是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千打架可厉害了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更科同学把人打飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千  都在看你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊上禁止跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更科同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学典礼穿立领的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被人说三道四了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打倒在地的人  鞋子是红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是二年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脏死…了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（确定座位）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  下一位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最前面  楼道旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}下一位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几号？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上起不来吗
