Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐那位置肯定会天天睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  离我家很近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长怎么定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都还不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用猜拳或者抽签更妥当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像个成熟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千打架可厉害了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉她与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同学笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得更科同学最适合做班长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真让我大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然叫自己小千
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉她好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟君笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}开始喽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪子布！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你说小千的坏话！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙  沙织并没有说她坏话的意思  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说她怪怪的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还不是坏话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己的性格也好不到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}手举起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  到此为止到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了桃子  来个深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（第三节体育课  换好衣服后到操场集合）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班变得好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  肚子饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生聚集在一起时  总觉得好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛偷偷摸摸地换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得跟女生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没吃到教训
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  上次被打还记着仇呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那你脸红什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}谁脸红了 眼睛长哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}是是  写在脸上了  都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算到了世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你肯定能活到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真穗的弟弟挺可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把气撒在饭上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一点也不臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你是真穗的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟的班级里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个叫千叶的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:07:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要参加社团活动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  也有直接回家的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师以前是哪个部的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}咦  你跟我一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美术部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}一起去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想过当美术老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…有个喜欢的女孩在才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这种理由不也挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻君是篮球部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想长高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起打篮球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙织叫我跟她去同一个部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  高槻君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家关系都好那该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级的前辈叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千打架惹出祸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是找千叶同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经打过招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但被前辈们无视了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去要去参观社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拽什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是打招呼什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶同学好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气势上完全胜过她们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是我告诉她们教室才弄成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得这不怪二鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然西丘第一小学很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那态度简直让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶沙织就是个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？小千喜欢那样的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级生集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道几点才能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说一年级生集合了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄错了  是篮球部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  沙织
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排球部还没集合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  篮球部和排球部在同一个地方练习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐同学真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢指导
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好久没三个人一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易分在同班  你们两个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要和你们绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝交…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好…  要和好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是佐佐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那么讨厌我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记恨着对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前把你的弟弟错当成女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你觉得修很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是修像我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直受小诚照顾  是一对的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你不觉得我们老师很棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概喜欢男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟不是这样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你喜欢高槻同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是要好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是千叶同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人活得真压抑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压抑？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是活着很压抑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着很压抑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等再去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小修先去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先洗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着很压抑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.52,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HB3DBD8&}9{\1c&HD6B7F9&}个{\1c&HD8E0C1&}月{\1c&HEDC0CC&}前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.27,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HB3DBD8&}佳{\1c&HD6B7F9&}乃{\1c&HD8E0C1&}的{\1c&HECD6BC&}房{\1c&HEDC0CC&}间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来问高槻同学的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟同学向你告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟说了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更类似于我逼他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说喜欢他  让他很困扰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真有默契
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会来这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不想见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来听招人讨厌的话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说过不知道来这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讨厌你这点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可说不出让讨厌自己的人喜欢自己这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有做什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分贝别这么高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天觉得自己最可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也是  把我当成坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  没和佳乃一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  加奈子今天很早就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有社团活动的晨练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真的生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  那就只好…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和千叶同学和好不就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想去教室啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直躲在保健室也不是办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气就说出绝交这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但身在同班要不说话  还是有难度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把保健室当作旅馆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的  那家伙真恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  今天有社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧  大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去社团吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今天不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概会被二年级盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要单独一人的好  绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同学  干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同学挺直腰杆这么说了那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我去叫佐佐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好帅  我也可以参加吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小千去的话  我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帅吗？桃子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没带钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子那份我来出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中生放学回家的路…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起回家的路…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟是如此的…如此的…开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓味  吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙织  你不吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有资格这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙织你又说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视她们的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家和她打招呼 是在无视我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信  那个一年级怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙织
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  那家伙性格恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明天陪你一起去道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  更科同学笑过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用笑得这么夸张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同学好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}小千差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟越来越喜欢她了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻君也说点什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！


